description: Eagle Graphite Incorporated, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of graphite properties in Canada. The company holds an interest in the Black Crystal project located in the city of Nelson in British Columbia. As of May 31, 2021, it owned 6 mineral tenures covering an area of approximately 1,412 hectares of land near Nelson, British Columbia. The company is based in Toronto, Canada.
